title: Press Release Issued on Possible Heavy Rainfall (City of Fredericksburg, TX)
text: ( Source : City of Fredericksburg, TX ) Posted on: October 23 , 2015 Press Release Issued on Possible Heavy Rainfall The National weather service has placed a large portion of Texas under a Flash Flood Watch . Flash flooding is probable
